# NEMETIC STRING
# Free_Will_Determinism (C148)

Φ(Free_Will_Determinism) = σ(autonomy|causality) ∘ ρ(agency|necessity) ∘ λ(evolution|fixity) ∘ β(culture|biology) ∘ δγ(responsibility|mechanism) ∘ μ(commitment|impulse) + ε | :compatibilist

# OPERATOR BREAKDOWN
# σ(autonomy|causality)        :: Air  :: Self-directed thought vs causal chains
# ρ(agency|necessity)          :: Water :: Fluid negotiation between acting and being acted upon
# λ(evolution|fixity)          :: Fire  :: Natural selection creating novel capacities; freedom evolves
# β(culture|biology)           :: Wood  :: Co-evolution of memes and genes
# δγ(responsibility|mechanism) :: Earth :: Moral accountability grounded in social practices
# μ(commitment|impulse)        :: Metal :: Structural capacity for self-control through pre-commitment
